OL,3,C'Get your steps in': Fans asked to
OL,4,Cwalk to final test event at new stadium
OL,6,FMerseytravel have told supporters to
OL,7,Fbe prepared to "get your steps in" as
OL,8,FEverton FC's new stadium tests at
OL,9,Fcapacity for first time.
OL,11,FThe Toffees will host Italian giants
OL,12,FAS Roma at Everton's new Hill
OL,13,FDickinson Stadium in a double-header
OL,14,Ffriendly match, with both clubs' first
OL,15,Fteams and legends facing off.
OL,17,FThe company have advised fans that
OL,18,FSandhills station is likely to be
OL,19,F"very busy", so have recommended that
OL,20,Ffans take the approximately 30-minute
OL,21,Fwalk from Moorfields station instead.
