OL,3,C'Get your steps in': Fans asked to
OL,4,Cwalk to final test event at new stadium
OL,6,FIt is the third and final test event
OL,7,Fat the stadium, and will be the first
OL,8,Ftime it will welcome a capacity crowd
OL,9,Fof up to 52,769.
OL,11,FMerseyrail say they have a "robust
OL,12,Fplan" in place for the fixture, with
OL,13,Fextra services and staff across the
OL,14,Fnetwork.
OL,16,FSandhills station will serve as the
OL,17,Fmain hub for match day travel, where a
OL,18,Fsecond entrance and pedestrian
OL,19,Ffootbridge has been constructed in an
OL,20,Fattempt to manage the crowds.
