OL,3,C'Get your steps in': Fans asked to
OL,4,Cwalk to final test event at new stadium
OL,6,FMoorfields and Bank Hall stations are
OL,7,Fbeing used as part of Merseyrail's
OL,8,Fcontingency plans, should disruption
OL,9,Foccur at Sandhills station during the
OL,10,Fevent.
OL,12,FFurther provisions for the fixture
OL,13,Finclude:
OL,15,FAfter the first test event, the
OL,16,FEverton Fans' Forum wrote an open
OL,17,Fletter to Liverpool Metro Mayor Steve
OL,18,FRotheram with concerns over transport,
OL,19,Fparking and street lighting near the
OL,20,Fclub's new stadium.
