OL,3,C'Get your steps in': Fans asked to
OL,4,Cwalk to final test event at new stadium
OL,6,FLong queues formed on platforms at
OL,7,FSandhills station, fans were unable to
OL,8,Fpark close by and a lack of street
OL,9,Flighting on nearby roads also caused
OL,10,Fissues.
OL,12,FNeil Grabham, Managing Director at
OL,13,FMerseyrail, said: "We look forward to
OL,14,Fwelcoming Everton fans who choose to
OL,15,Ftravel by Merseyrail to this weekend's
OL,16,Fthird test event at the Hill Dickinson
OL,17,FStadium.
