OL,6,F"We've put in place a robust plan with
OL,7,Fextra services and staff across the
OL,8,Fnetwork to support, but customers
OL,9,Fshould expect the network to be very
OL,10,Fbusy on Saturday.
OL,12,F"Like train stations near other major
OL,13,Ffootball stadiums across the UK,
OL,14,FSandhills station will be extremely
OL,15,Fbusy on matchdays.
OL,17,F"Customers can help us, to help them,
OL,18,Fby planning ahead, allowing extra time
OL,19,Ffor journeys, and considering
OL,20,Falternative routes in case of
OL,21,Funexpected disruption".
