OL,3,C'Get your steps in': Fans asked to
OL,4,Cwalk to final test event at new stadium
OL,6,FThe men's team played their final
OL,7,Fmatch at Goodison Park on 18 May 2025
OL,8,Fwhen they beat Southampton 2-0.
OL,10,FThe new ground is built on Bramley
OL,11,FMoore Dock, and takes its name from
OL,12,Fthe international commercial law firm
OL,13,F"Hill Dickinson" based in Liverpool,
OL,14,Fwho are the official naming rights
OL,15,Fpartner.
OL,17,FThe Toffees will host their first
OL,18,FPremier League match at Hill Dickinson
OL,19,FStadium on Sunday 24 August against
OL,20,FBrighton and Hove Albion.
